Introduction

Bryn is a South Korean rapper under Kaich and Brynshomelab who debuted independently in 2018 with the single "HAZY CITY". She was the oldest and the only female member of the DiCKIDS crew, now disbanded. She started music when she was in middle school, but did not gain public recognition until 2017, when her crew became popular after the first season of Mnet's High School Rapper.

She participated on Mnet rap survival show Show Me The Money on seasons 6 and 8, where she became the first ever female rapper on the show to make it to the top 8.
